assistant: 1. Move to the kitchen counter.
2. Identify the jar of jam on the counter.
3. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for jam.
4. Put the jar of jam in its standard storage location.
5. Identify the box of Jello on the counter.
6. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for Jello.
7. Put the box of Jello in its standard storage location.
8. Identify the box of Alpen Salt on the counter.
9. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for Alpen Salt.
10. Put the box of Alpen Salt in its standard storage location.
11. Identify the box of Rice Bubbles on the counter.
12. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for Rice Bubbles.
13. Put the box of Rice Bubbles in its standard storage location.
14. Identify the second jar of jam on the counter.
15. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for jam.
16. Put the second jar of jam in its standard storage location.
17. Identify the box of shortbread cookies on the counter.
18. Open a kitchen cabinet to locate the standard storage location for shortbread cookies.
19. Put the box of shortbread cookies in its standard storage location.
20. Identify the stack of plates on the counter.
21. Open a kitchen cabinet or the cabinet above the counter to locate the standard storage location for plates.
22. Put the stack of plates in its standard storage location.
23. Move to the dining area.
24. Identify the milk bottle on the table.
25. Open the refrigerator to locate the standard storage location for milk.
26. Put the milk bottle in the refrigerator.
27. Identify the second bottle of water on the table.
28. Open the refrigerator to locate the standard storage location for water.
29. Put the bottle of water in the refrigerator.
30. Identify the cookbook on the table.
31. Open a kitchen cabinet or a bookshelf if available to locate the standard storage location for the cookbook.
32. Put the cookbook in its standard storage location.
33. Identify the puzzle box on the table.
34. Open a kitchen cabinet or a drawer to locate the standard storage location for the puzzle box.
35. Put the puzzle box in its standard storage location.
